atched non-fraud controls. Include repeated runs/tolerance bands if model output is non-deterministic.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.02,"Integration":0.13,"System":0.05,"Agentic":0.72,"Workflow":0.08}},{"behavior_id":3,"description":"The velocity check in the scoring model correctly counts the number of transactions within the configured time window per user.","minimum_level":"Integration","justification":"MOCK-MISS: yes — pure unit tests can miss repository/query/window-boundary bugs. REAL-INFRA: local DB/filesystem-backed store is sufficient; no external API required. MOCK-HIDE: yes — mocked transaction history can hide timestamp filtering and per-user partition errors. LLM-DEP: no. MULTI-STEP: no.","test_description":"Seed a local transaction store with timestamped records around the exact window boundaries for multiple users. Run the real velocity-check path and assert only in-window transactions for the target user are counted, including edge cases at boundary timestamps and out-of-order inserts.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.2,"Integration":0.65,"System":0.1,"Agentic":0.03,"Workflow":0.02}},{"behavior_id":4,"description":"A transaction flagged by the risk model but not by the scoring model is still held for review — the models operate as an OR gate, not AND.","minimum_level":"Integration","justification":"MOCK-MISS: yes — unit-testing an isolated boolean helper may miss service-layer wiring where model outputs are merged. REAL-INFRA: no external systems required; compose real scoring + risk result handlers in-process. MOCK-HIDE: yes — over-mocked adapters can bypass real orchestration defects. LLM-DEP: not required here because the condition can be driven by fixed model outputs at interface boundaries. MULTI-STEP: no.","test_description":"Run the transaction decision pipeline with real aggregation/orchestration modules, injecting deterministic model resu